Subject: [PATCH] sched/topology: Assert non-NUMA topology masks don't
 (partially) overlap
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit
References: bnc#1012628
